cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.SE, cs.CR 

This paper deals with an extension of temporal epistemic logic that includes operators for quantifying over agent strategies. The paper discusses examples related to game theory, knowledge-based programs, and computer security policies, which are all topics that are commonly studied in the sub-categories of logic (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), game theory (cs.GT), software engineering (cs.SE), and computer security (cs.CR). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
